  "secondName": "The Walking Storm",
  "description": "Though most people value harmony over strife, Imran was always the opposite. Even as a child, he was always caught up in some kind of fight. As soon as he was old enough to participate in wars against neighboring clans, it was clear that Imran was to become the greatest warrior of the Dust Steppes.\n\nHowever, he soon tired of defeating fellow humans, so he turned to hunting down vicious monsters for a greater challenge. One day, he tracked down the whereabouts of a legendary dragon, but even he was no match against it. However, the dragon found a kindred spirit in the ever battle hungry Imran, and they agreed to have a rematch some day.",
